Verify Preconditions
Instructions: 1) Make sure all the preconditions listed are met. They will be required by upcoming tests. 2) At least one contact has to exist on the phone. (contact with the ID '47' will be used) 3) At least one calendar item has to exist on the phone. (calender item with the ID '1' will be used) 4) At least one MISSED call has to exist on the phone. 5) Click 'GO' to start testing.
Expected behaviour: See green colored line on the device screen.
